OL,3,C'Little evidence of training':
OL,4,CBrothers convicted after industrial
OL,5,Csite death
OL,7,FTwo brothers have been found guilty
OL,8,Ffor their roles in the death of a man
OL,9,Fwho died on an industrial site in
OL,10,FBirmingham.
OL,12,FAko Azizpour, 27, died on 8 February
OL,13,F2024, after police were called to UK
OL,14,FSuperior Glass on Tyburn Road,
OL,15,FErdington. First responders found Mr
OL,16,FAzizpour had been attempting to unload
OL,17,Fcrates of glass from a container when
OL,18,Fhe became trapped - although urgent
OL,19,Fwork began to free him, he was
OL,20,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
