FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782908305
OL,3,C'Little evidence of training':
OL,4,CBrothers convicted after industrial
OL,5,Csite death
OL,7,FNashwan Amin, 29, of Garrard Gardens,
OL,8,FSutton Coldfield, was found guilty of
OL,9,Fgross negligence manslaughter, having
OL,10,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to
OL,11,Fperverting to the course of justice.
OL,13,FHis brother, Razwan Amin, 27, of
OL,14,FWildmoor Close, Redditch, had
OL,15,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fperverting the course of justice.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
