OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782908305
OL,3,C'Little evidence of training':
OL,4,CBrothers convicted after industrial
OL,5,Csite death
OL,7,FAn inspection of the premises found
OL,8,Fnothing in the way of documentation
OL,9,Frelating to employees or health and
OL,10,Fsafety, and little evidence of
OL,11,Ftraining, according to West Midlands
OL,12,FPolice and the Health and Safety
OL,13,FExecutive (HSE).
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782908305
OL,3,C'Little evidence of training':
OL,4,CBrothers convicted after industrial
OL,5,Csite death
OL,7,FIt also noted the glass which had been
OL,8,Fdelivered had a total weight of more
OL,9,Fthan 24,000 kilograms, and was shipped
OL,10,Fin 11 separate crates, each weighing
OL,11,Fover two tonnes. The report stated
OL,12,Fthese should have been unloaded by a
OL,13,Fcrane or specialised forklift ` but
OL,14,Fthe business owner had neither.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782908305
OL,3,C'Little evidence of training':
OL,4,CBrothers convicted after industrial
OL,5,Csite death
OL,7,FNashwan Amin, the person registered as
OL,8,Fhaving significant control of UK
OL,9,FSuperior Glass, was arrested the
OL,10,Ffollowing week, having previously
OL,11,Fprovided a statement in relation to
OL,12,Fthe incident which was found to be
OL,13,Fwholly inaccurate.
OL,15,FThe police found evidence that
OL,16,Fsuggested he knew a crane or forklift
OL,17,Fwould be required to lift the glass
OL,18,Fbut had made no arrangements for
OL,19,Feither.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782908305
OL,3,C'Little evidence of training':
OL,4,CBrothers convicted after industrial
OL,5,Csite death
OL,7,FA further report from HSE stated that
OL,8,Fspecialised equipment would have been
OL,9,Fneeded to unload it, and the risk of
OL,10,Fdeath within the danger zone around
OL,11,Fthe crates was highly foreseeable.
OL,13,FDetectives also found evidence that
OL,14,FNashwan Amin had been targeting people
OL,15,Flocally who were seeking asylum,
OL,16,Frecruiting them to work for him as a
OL,17,Fcheap form of labour.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782908305
OL,3,C'Little evidence of training':
OL,4,CBrothers convicted after industrial
OL,5,Csite death
OL,7,FAt Birmingham Crown Court yesterday
OL,8,F(30 June), Nashwan Amin, was found
OL,9,Fguilty of gross negligence
OL,10,Fmanslaughter and perverting the course
OL,11,Fof justice.
OL,13,FHe was remanded into custody and is
OL,14,Fdue to be sentenced on 17 September.
OL,16,FDet Chief Inspector Daniel Jarratt,
OL,17,Fwho led the investigation, said: "This
OL,18,Fhas been a complex investigation
OL,19,Fthroughout which our thoughts have
OL,20,Fremained with Mr Azizpour's family.
OL,26,@yD@bOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782908305
OL,3,C'Little evidence of training':
OL,4,CBrothers convicted after industrial
OL,5,Csite death
OL,7,F"We worked closely with the Health and
OL,8,FSafety Executive, and we were able to
OL,9,Ffind out what happened that day ` and
OL,10,Fdemonstrate that ultimately Mr
OL,11,FAzizpour's death could have been
OL,12,Fprevented.
OL,14,F"We were committed to bringing the
OL,15,Fpair to justice, and employers must be
OL,16,Freminded to uphold their duty of care,
OL,17,Fespecially where lives are lost due to
OL,18,Fpreventable negligence."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
