OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782908305
OL,3,C'Little evidence of training':
OL,4,CBrothers convicted after industrial
OL,5,Csite death
OL,7,FThroughout the investigation and
OL,8,Fsubsequent legal process, Mr
OL,9,FAzizpour's family have been supported
OL,10,Fby specialist officers.
OL,12,FIn a statement released last year,
OL,13,Fthey said it was still difficult to
OL,14,Fbelieve they had lost their son, and
OL,15,Fthey demanded justice over his death.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/9
